name: folium
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.2.1" %}

package:
  name: folium
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: folium-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.python.org/packages/source/f/folium/folium-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 6b267b43e573b4f1d6317501f612e5aef92d6965c454ebe8ab73f259d9859107

build:
  number: 1
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python
    - jinja2
    - numpy
    - pandas
    - vincent

test:
  imports:
    - folium

about:
  home: https://github.com/python-visualization/folium
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: 'Make beautiful maps with Leaflet.js and Python.'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ocefpaf
    - BibMartin

about.summary: Make beautiful maps with Leaflet.js and Python.
